The hotel is part of Canadian chain hotels which are 3 stars but I think this hotel is 3.5 or 4 stars.	The location is ok, but I wouldn't stay here again, primarily because of the standard of service.	The room was moderately spaced but was decorated beautifully and everything looked brand new.	It was one of the cheaper options but we were assured it was a good standard and the fact it was a suite as opposed to a room swayed our decision.	The bedroom in the standard room is pretty small.	The bedroom and bathroom is small but it wasnt a big deal to me at all.